    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone comfortable with some cosmetic and minor mechanical needs. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster. While it runs and drives, it will soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and tires. This is an honest, high-mileage car that still has life left but isn't a showpiece.",
