    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in a fantastic vehicle that perfectly balances quality and value! This car is in good condition, showing it has been well-cared for with a smooth ride and a clean, inviting interior. It's a reliable choice that's ready for many more miles of dependable service\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a solid, honest car!",
